with a major impact on functioning in the workplace, or through an extensive examination.</p><ul><li>The <strong>VOP </strong><strong>of indefinite duration </strong>is granted to employees with a long-term persistent problem.</li><li>The VOP of <strong>definite duration</strong> is awarded to employees whose condition is or may be evolving positively or for whom the prognosis is unclear.</li></ul><h3>Premium application</h3><p>After approval of the work restriction (after which the employee receives a confirmation e-mail from VDAB), the employer can apply via the<br>WSE desk to <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/economie-en-ondernemen/personeel/vlaamse-ondersteuningspremie-vop/vlaamse-ondersteuningspremie-opvolgen\">apply for the support premium from DWSE</a>.</p><p>If the application is approved, the VOP is paid into the company's bank account number at the <strong>end of each quarter</strong>. The company receives the premium each time for the previous quarter.</p><p>The employer and employee consider together how best to use the premium.</p>"},"@type":"Procedure","order":0}],"websites":[{"naam":{"nl":"Vlaamse ondersteuningspremie (VOP) (Vlaanderen.be)","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Vlaamse ondersteuningspremie (VOP) (Vlaanderen.be)","nl-BE-x-formal":"Vlaamse ondersteuningspremie (VOP) (Vlaanderen.be)","en-x-generated":"Flemish support premium (VOP) (Vlaanderen.be)"},"url":"https://www.vlaanderen.be/vlaamse-ondersteuningspremie","@type":"Website","order":0}],"financieleVoordelen":[{"beschrijving":{"en":"<p>As an employer, you will receive a subsidy every three months for five years. You can then apply for an extension.</p><p>On the website you can read <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/economie-en-ondernemen/personeel/vlaamse-ondersteuningspremie-vop/vlaamse-ondersteuningspremie-uitbetaling-belastingen-en-cumulaties\">how the amount of the VOP is determined</a>.</p>","nl":"<p>De VOP wordt aan het eind van het volgende kwartaal uitbetaald volgens dit sc